  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Preliminary Efficacy of AV411 in Neuropathic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Trial of AV411 to Assess Its Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Preliminary Efficacy in the Treatment of Neuropathic Pain</official_title>
