  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, tolerability and pharmacokinetics of
      AV411 after single and multiple doses in patients with chronic neuropathic pain due to
      diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
